The paper discusses distance metric learning (DML) for high dimensional data, which is a common problem in machine learning and computer vision. - cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): This sub-category covers topics related to computer vision, which often involves high dimensional data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): This sub-category covers topics related to artificial intelligence, which includes machine learning and computer vision. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): This sub-category covers topics related to data structures and algorithms, which are relevant to the proposed method involving random projection.
